snippet.title: Bugdom - Level 1
snippet.description:
this is bugdom, a video game for the apple os made in 1999. this game was my fucking childhood and i noticed there were no other regular playthroughs of it before uploading this, so i had to upload my own

i don't know why i didn't pick up any of the green clovers, don't ask
